Troubleshooting Common Issues
Issue 1: auditd Service Not Starting
Solution:

sudo systemctl reset-failed auditd
sudo systemctl start auditd
sudo systemctl status auditd
Issue 2: Permission Denied Errors
Solution:

# Ensure proper permissions for monitoring directories
chmod 755 /home/$USER/secure_files
# Run audit commands with sudo
sudo auditctl -l
Issue 3: No Audit Events Generated
Solution:

# Check if audit rules are properly set
sudo auditctl -l
# Verify auditd is logging
sudo tail -f /var/log/audit/audit.log
Issue 4: Script Execution Errors
Solution:

# Ensure scripts are executable
chmod +x *.sh
# Check for syntax errors
bash -n script_name.sh
